{"title":"迎春曲","authors":["柯仲平"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":2,"day":8}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎春曲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"柯仲平"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们是谁？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看！我们把东风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"作成号来吹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把春雷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"作成鼓来擂；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们戴春的花披春的光辉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们舞起千条山，万条水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"舞得山见我们就点头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水见我们就摆尾；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田地看见我们就笑就张嘴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们把田地喂的一天比一天肥。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们舞得沙滩也变成金银滩，——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哈哈！那像一张大羊皮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"裹着满天的宝贝！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们是谁？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们一定，东风把西风完全压倒，春雷把乌云彻底粉碎！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们在社会主义世界里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们是一支劳动的歌舞大队！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}